data.description: You will fall in love with this cute 3 bedroom home conveniently located near Saluda Shoals, Harbison Boulevard, and Lake Murray.  Not to mention the pool in the large backyard.  This home is also ecofriendly with solar panels that generate an amazing amount of solar that saves with electric costs!  This home also features new carpet, fenced backyard, newly painted walls, and new windows. Kitchen appliances included. Schedule a tour of this home and you won't be disappointed!
